{"tid":2072180,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"係邊條撚樣宣揚領養代替購買？","createTime":"2020-06-20T11:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T16:42:40.000Z","uid":5737,"like":86,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f41675a43bb6dd8f8e16057a1576960df2ca55f8","tid":2072180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"就係你地班仆街 唔正視香港根本既問題 <br />\n令到無人關注動物條例<br />\n個個都淨係識講領養代替購買 <br />\n根本就係要訂立更完善既寵物保護同販賣條例<br />\n以為領養完就幫到寵物店啲貓貓狗狗？<br />\n你唔買大把人買，到最後無人買會去邊？<br />\n係比班黑店老闆賤賣返上支那比班支那畜生食阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上香港個班所謂既貓義工，<br />\n間接做左幫兇 刺激左買賣寵物<br />\n你地班口上面掛住領養代替購買既人<br />\n以後咪撚再宣揚呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n要真正從根本解決呢樣問題 <br />\n同真正幫到啲貓貓狗狗既<br />\n唔該，加強監管販賣寵物及保護寵物條例<br />\n係呢方面香港既法例真係太落後，<br />\n令太多無良既商人同黑店行到灰色地帶！<br />\n<br />\n希望推上去令更多人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw鄺神同毛姨姨係咪有關注呢方面既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfc89f255046a23e109e8b6d0bc076d14c15785","tid":2072180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f4a3ca4a62621b43cd07dd5eeb460c5901bbbb3","tid":2072180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6acba55737f8798ca5e8565554ef9086871b7b6","tid":2072180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6d63a13247d39688c0199068325ca7e0e3bc949","tid":2072180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5044af1e92d9631cfedc156af11c1c28ceeac2de","tid":2072180,"uid":119761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa65913a85bd8b87df5f779af7d6160abc44fd24","tid":2072180,"uid":49457,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"